       <h2>More About Tailor Management System</h2>
       <hr>
       <h3>
       Tailor management system with Design Recommendation will suggest the appropriate design of cloth to the user based on the content-based recommendation system. It will overcome the problems seen in the tailoring business. The daily tasks of the tailoring business are automated by this system. This will be especially beneficial for shirting suiting tailors, but any other tailor shops can also use it. In overall, Tailor management system with Design Recommendation is the project title. This system will solve the tailoring business problems and help to grow the business.
       
       <br>
       <br>
       1. User Management System:
       <br>
       This system acts as a pivotal management hub of the company as it allows the administrator to perform the necessary task related to the management of the staff’s profile. This system allows the administrator to manipulate the staff’s profile and account as well as changing the necessary improvement. It also allows the administrator to see through various details regarding staff’s profile such as salary and personal details. It allows the staff to view personal details.
       <br>
       <br>
       2. Customer Management System:
       <br>
       This system allows the company to manage and analyze every potential data regarding the ever past and current customer. It allows the company to store and edit the necessary data in past. It also allows the company to analyze customer valuation.
       <br>
       <br>
       3. Product Management System:
       <br>
       This system acts as a record keeper for monitoring and maintaining the company inventories. It keeps tabs on stocked products, company assets, raw material, and supplies.
       <br>
       <br>
       4.Order Management System:
       <br>
       The order management system is a system that keeps tabs on the customer order. It also allows the user to create, edit and cancel the order of the customer. It helps the user to track its order through choosing, stitching, packing until the delivery. It also sends the email to the customer when the order is completed.
       <br>
       <br>
       5.Finance Management System:
       <br>
       The financial Management system allows the company to govern its income, expense, loss, and profit etc. It works intending to maintain the company daily business activities as well as ensuring the company is making maximum profits.
       <br>
       <br>
       6.Recommendation System:
       <br>
       This system works closely with the customer. It helps to recommend better products to the customer based on user preference.
